short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Deltapath Talk - Integration for Web Browsers

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Deltapath Talk is an extension on Google Chrome to enable you to perform click to dial or create automatically screen pop of desired web applications on incoming call.
